# Hostamar Slack + PagerDuty Alert Templates

## P1: VRAM > 85% (Critical)

### Slack Message
```
🚨 P1 · VRAM CRITICAL
GPU VRAM at {value}% on RTX 5060

Loaded models: {models}
Circuit breakers: {breaker_states}
OOM errors (5m): {oom_count}

Runbook: docs/runbooks/oncall-runbook.md#oom
Executor: scripts/runbook-executor.ps1 -Incident oom -AutoFix

@on-call-infra
```

### PagerDuty Payload
```json
{
  "routing_key": "{PAGERDUTY_SERVICE_KEY}",
  "event_action": "trigger",
  "dedup_key": "vram-critical-{{labels.instance}}",
  "payload": {
    "summary": "VRAM > 85% on RTX 5060",
    "severity": "critical",
    "source": "Grafana",
    "component": "gpu",
    "group": "infrastructure",
    "class": "oom",
    "custom_details": {
      "vram_percent": "{{ $value }}",
      "loaded_models": "{{ models }}",
      "oom_5m": "{{ oom_count }}",
      "runbook": "docs/runbooks/oncall-runbook.md#oom"
    }
  },
  "images": [{
    "src": "{{ grafana_panel_url }}",
    "alt": "VRAM Usage Panel"
  }]
}
```

### Escalation
- 0-5 min: On-call infra → runbook executor
- 5-10 min: Infra lead → evaluate full unload
- 10+ min: Engineering manager → cloud failover decision

