## P1: Docker Model Runner Down

### Slack Message
```
🚨 P1 · DMR DOWN
Docker Model Runner unreachable.

Status: {status}
Fallback: Ollama at localhost:11434 — {ollama_status}
Downtime: {duration}

Runbook: docs/runbooks/oncall-runbook.md#dmr-down
Executor: scripts/runbook-executor.ps1 -Incident dmr-down -AutoFix

@on-call-infra
```

### PagerDuty Payload
```json
{
  "routing_key": "{PAGERDUTY_SERVICE_KEY}",
  "event_action": "trigger",
  "dedup_key": "dmr-down-{{labels.instance}}",
  "payload": {
    "summary": "Docker Model Runner is down",
    "severity": "critical",
    "source": "Grafana",
    "component": "dmr",
    "group": "infrastructure",
    "class": "service_down",
    "custom_details": {
      "dmr_status": "unreachable",
      "ollama_status": "{{ ollama_status }}",
      "duration": "{{ duration }}",
      "runbook": "docs/runbooks/oncall-runbook.md#dmr-down"
    }
  }
}
```

### Escalation
- 0-5 min: On-call infra → docker model stop/start
- 5-10 min: Infra lead → Docker Desktop restart
- 10+ min: CTO → cloud-only mode declaration

