## P2: Circuit Breaker Open

### Slack Message
```
⚠️ P2 · CIRCUIT BREAKER OPEN
{count} breaker(s) open for: {models}

Failures (24h): {failure_count}
Last error: {last_error}

Reset: scripts/runbook-executor.ps1 -Incident circuit-breaker -ModelName <model>

@on-call-infra
```

### PagerDuty Payload
```json
{
  "routing_key": "{PAGERDUTY_SERVICE_KEY}",
  "event_action": "trigger",
  "dedup_key": "cb-open-{{labels.model}}",
  "payload": {
    "summary": "Circuit breaker open for {{labels.model}}",
    "severity": "warning",
    "source": "Grafana",
    "component": "model",
    "group": "ai",
    "class": "circuit_breaker",
    "custom_details": {
      "model": "{{labels.model}}",
      "failure_count": "{{ failure_count }}"
    }
  }
}
```

### Escalation
- 0-15 min: On-call infra → evaluate and reset
- 15+ min: Infra lead → investigate root cause

