## P2: Brute Force Login

### Slack Message
```
⚠️ P2 · BRUTE FORCE DETECTED
Login failure rate: {rate}/min
Blocked IPs: {blocked_ips}

Source IPs: {ip_list}
Admin email targeted: {target}

Runbook: docs/runbooks/incident-runbook.md#login-brute-force

@on-call-security
```

### PagerDuty Payload
```json
{
  "routing_key": "{PAGERDUTY_SERVICE_KEY}",
  "event_action": "trigger",
  "dedup_key": "bruteforce-{{source_ip}}",
  "payload": {
    "summary": "Brute force login detected",
    "severity": "warning",
    "source": "Grafana",
    "component": "auth",
    "group": "security",
    "class": "brute_force"
  }
}
```

### Escalation
- 0-15 min: On-call security → verify IP blocks
- 15+ min: Security lead → permanent blocklist + law enforcement report

