## Grafana Alert Notification Channel Setup

### Slack Webhook
```json
{
  "type": "slack",
  "settings": {
    "url": "https://hooks.slack.com/services/{TEAM}/{TOKEN}",
    "recipient": "#hostamar-alerts"
  }
}
```

### PagerDuty Integration
```json
{
  "type": "pagerduty",
  "settings": {
    "integrationKey": "{PAGERDUTY_SERVICE_KEY}",
    "severity": "critical"
  }
}
```

### Alertmanager (if using Prometheus)
```yaml
receivers:
  - name: 'slack-p1'
    slack_configs:
      - channel: '#hostamar-alerts'
        title: '🚨 {{ .GroupLabels.alertname }}'
        text: '{{ .CommonAnnotations.description }}'
        send_resolved: true
  - name: 'pagerduty-p1'
    pagerduty_configs:
      - routing_key: '{PAGERDUTY_SERVICE_KEY}'
        severity: critical
        description: '{{ .CommonAnnotations.summary }}'
```
